# ZelCandy

Shared configuration and path management for Zel CLI tools.

## Installation

### Quick Install (Recommended)

Install to default location:
```bash
curl -sSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Zeldean/zelcandy/main/bootstrap-zel.py | python3
```

### Custom Install Location

Install to a specific directory:
```bash
curl -sSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Zeldean/zelcandy/main/bootstrap-zel.py | python3 - --install-dir ~/my-zel-tools
```

### Default Locations

**Installation Directory:**
- Linux/macOS: `~/.local/share/zel-tools`
- Windows: `%LOCALAPPDATA%\zel-tools`

**Virtual Environment:**
- Linux/macOS: `~/.local/share/zel-env`
- Windows: `%LOCALAPPDATA%\zel-env`

### Manual Installation

1. Clone the repository:
```bash
git clone https://github.com/Zeldean/zelcandy.git
cd zelcandy
```

2. Run the install script:
```bash
python3 src/zelcandy/install.py
```

## Usage

### Path Management

```bash
# Set paths
zelcandy path set vault /mnt/Vault/Second-Brain
zelcandy path set budget-data ~/Documents/Budget

# List paths
zelcandy path list

# Get a path
zelcandy path get vault
```

### Module Management

```bash
# List available modules
zelcandy install list

# Install all modules
zelcandy install all

# Install specific module (from GitHub)
zelcandy install module zeltimer
```
